    "id": "nce2-010-not-for-jazz",
    "title": "Lesson 10: Not for Jazz",
    "audioFilename": "10－Not for Jazz.mp3",
    "duration": 63.06,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.08,
      "end": 1.34,
      "text": "Lesson 10.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第10课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 2.36,
      "end": 3.42,
      "text": "Not for Jazz.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "不适合演奏爵士乐。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 5.08,
      "end": 7.92,
      "text": "listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 9.06,
      "end": 11.1,
      "text": "What happened to the clavichord?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "那架古钢琴发生了什么事？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 12.62,
      "end": 15.22,
      "text": "We have an old musical instrument.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我们有一件古老的乐器。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 16.06,
      "end": 18,
      "text": "It is called a clavichord.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "它叫古钢琴。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 18.92,
      "end": 22.3,
      "text": "It was made in Germany in 1681.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "它于1681年在德国制造。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 23.8,
      "end": 26.06,
      "text": "Our clavichord is kept in the living room.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我们的古钢琴存放在客厅里。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 27.18,
      "end": 35.54,
      "text": "It has belonged to our family for a long time. The instrument was bought by my grandfather many years ago.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "它属于我们家已经很久了。这件乐器是我祖父多年前买的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 36.58,
      "end": 39.02,
      "text": "Recently it was damaged by a visitor.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "最近它被一位客人弄坏了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 39.88,
      "end": 42.22,
      "text": "She tried to play jazz on it.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "她试图用它演奏爵士乐。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 42.88,
      "end": 47.3,
      "text": "She struck the keys too hard and two of the strings were broken.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "她敲键太用力，弄断了两根琴弦。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 48.4,
      "end": 50.12,
      "text": "My father was shocked.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我父亲大为震惊。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 51.24,
      "end": 53.72,
      "text": "Now we are not allowed to touch it.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "现在不许我们碰它。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 54.3,
      "end": 57.08,
      "text": "It is being repaired by a friend of my father's.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "父亲的一位朋友正在修理它。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
